examples.en: She has been ailing for years.
The actress's big break came when she substituted for the ailing star.
She wanted to take the trip, but was handcuffed by her responsibility to watch her ailing father.
They kept vigil at their ailing son's bedside the entire time he was in the hospital.
Though he was loath to take over the family business, he couldn't refuse his ailing father's adjuration.
